author: Atomic Shrimp
description:
This is a video that I have been intending to make for 7 years - but now, it's finally time to revisit Palm Nut Soup.

The recipe I made in this video was significantly influenced by this one (which uses a different palm soup product): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q79nwCfFo4k

The Fufu is based on what I learned from this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qaVhde4qXIA

Episode 46 of Weird Stuff in a Can is here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T2xqnHDhSiA

Babatunde's Red Oil video is here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GBL_UGKttqY

My spoon carving video is here: https://youtu.be/2iNK7t0MWRU

More information on Oil Palm: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elaeis_guineensis

More information on Kpakpo Shito peppers: https://www.modernghana.com/news/1282928/kpakposhito-improves-life-spans.html

Join the Atomic Shrimp official Discord server for FREE early access to videos! - https://discord.gg/atomicshrimp
Atomic Shrimp subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/AtomicShrimp/
